    "en": {
      "title": "The body of the child who was grabbed by the crocodile is found",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A group of Navy divers found the body of the seven-year-old school student who was snatched by a crocodile in the Kandalam Bow breakwater in a deep hole of more than twenty feet on the 16th at around ten in the morning at 10.45.",
        "On the morning of the 15th, while the mother went swimming with her father and sister, this child was grabbed by a crocodile while hanging on to the father's hand.",
        "The search operations for the child continued from that moment until now, then the Sigiriya Police brought a group of divers from the Navy and while conducting search operations in the lake, the body of the child was found in the middle of the lake in a depth of twenty 25 feet. The body was bitten by the crocodile. Being able to see injuries is a special feature."
      ],
